罗杰（达尔特雷）</a>做了一件令人难以置信的事情，他用电缆旋转麦克风，然后敲击钹。距离他身后大约 50 英尺，他就在镲片上击中了”。</p><p>凯奇继续说道：“我非常惊讶，当音乐会结束时，我就说‘是的！’我表弟认为我很荒谬，因为我太兴奋了，无法坐在座位上。但我只是被那个节目震惊了”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicolas-cages-son-wes-announces-new-solo-single-the-wolf-3478389">尼古拉斯·凯奇 (Nicolas Cage) 的儿子韦斯 (Wes) 宣布新的个人单曲《The Wolf》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
希里安·墨菲透露乌克兰入侵对《奥本海默》演员阵容的影响https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-reveals-impact-of-ukraine-invasion-on-oppenheimer-cast-3478337?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=cillian-murphy-reveals-impact-奥本海默演员表上的乌克兰入侵Chris EdwardsFri, 04 Aug 2023 14:02:01 +0000 Film NewsNewsCillian Murphyhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3478337 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥本海默" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “它无处不在，我们完全意识到这一点”</p><p>希里安<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-reveals-impact-of-ukraine-invasion-on-oppenheimer-cast-3478337">·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 揭露乌克兰入侵对《奥本海默》演员阵容的影响的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥本海默" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>希里安·墨菲透露了<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer">奥本海默</a>的演员阵容如何受到俄罗斯入侵乌克兰的影响。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">《奥本海默》评论：克里斯托弗·诺兰令人兴奋的传记片像一颗炸弹一样击中大脑</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位演员在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰</a>广受好评的电影中饰演罗伯特·J·奥本海默，一位现实生活中的美国物理学家，在原子弹的制造过程中发挥了关键作用。</p><p>墨菲在接受<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/cillian-murphy-interview-oppenheimer-3470442"><em>《NME》</em></a>独家采访时解释了演员们如何高度关注乌克兰发生的事件，尤其是在俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京通过在其边境布设战术核导弹来回应国际制裁之后。</p><p> “它无处不在，我们完全意识到这一点，”墨菲谈到入侵时说道。 “The threat [of nuclear war] has escalated and receded over the years since 1945… and now it&#39;s back. It&#39;s always there, this <a href="https://www.history.com/news/what-was-the-sword-of-damocles" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sword Of Damocles</a> that is hanging over us.” </p><figure id="attachment_3470625" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3470625" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3470625" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Cillian_Murphy_Seated.jpg" alt="希里安·墨菲" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Cillian_Murphy_Seated.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Cillian_Murphy_Seated-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Cillian_Murphy_Seated-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Cillian_Murphy_Seated-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Cillian_Murphy_Seated-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Cillian_Murphy_Seated-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3470625" class="wp-caption-text"> Cillian Murphy. CREDIT: Marco Grob</figcaption></figure><p> Elsewhere in the interview, Murphy admitted that he didn&#39;t socialise much while filming Oppenheimer, due to the intense demands of his role.</p><p> “I didn&#39;t go out much. I didn&#39;t socialise much, mainly because of the amount of work I had to do… I became so immersed in the role.”</p><p> The actor also explained how Nolan helped him to “unlock” the character with an “amazing phrase”.</p><p> “Chris used this amazing phrase. We were talking about Oppenheimer&#39;s arc and he said, &#39;You know, he&#39;s dancing between the raindrops morally.&#39; That unlocked something in my mind when I was preparing,” he recalled.</p><p> Murphy further explained of Oppenheimer: “I do think that he believed it would be the weapon to end all wars. He thought that [having the bomb] would motivate countries to form a sort of nuclear world governance. He was naive.” </p><figure id="attachment_3474889" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3474889" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3474889" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie.jpg" alt="奥本海默" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3474889" class="wp-caption-text"> Benny Safdie and Cillian Murphy in &#39;Oppenheimer&#39;. CREDIT: Universal Pictures</figcaption></figure><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad2 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><p> Alongside Murphy, <em>Oppenheimer</em> stars Emily Blunt, Matt Damon, Robert Downey Jr., Florence Pugh, Josh Hartnett, Benny Safdie, Casey Affleck, Rami Malek and Kenneth Branagh.</p><p> In a <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">five-star review of the film</a> , <em>NME</em> said: “Not just the definitive account of the man behind the atom bomb, <em>Oppenheimer</em> is a monumental achievement in grown-up filmmaking.</p><p> “For years, Nolan has been perfecting the art of the serious blockbuster – crafting smart, finely-tuned multiplex epics that demand attention; that can&#39;t be watched anywhere other than in a cinema, uninterrupted, without distractions. But this, somehow, feels bigger.”</p></div><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-reveals-impact-of-ukraine-invasion-on-oppenheimer-cast-3478337">Cillian Murphy reveals impact of Ukraine invasion on &#39;Oppenheimer&#39; cast</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
